'''Evergreen'''是一個[[開放原始碼|開放原始碼]]（[[GNU通用公共許可證|GNU通用公共許可證]]）的[[圖書館自動化|圖書館自動化]]（ILS），讀者可以[[萬維網|萬維網]]實現圖書的查找和借閱，許多北美的[[圖書館|圖書館]]都使用它。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.libraryjournal.com/article/CA6396354.html |title=Evergreen: Your Homegrown ILS |accessdate=2010-11-28 |archive-date=2011-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110409194920/http://www.libraryjournal.com/article/CA6396354.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blog.libraryjournal.com/ljinsider/2010/10/04/king-county-goes-live-with-customized-evergreen-ils/# |title=King County Goes Live with Customized Evergreen ILS |access-date=2010-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101010114646/http://blog.libraryjournal.com/ljinsider/2010/10/04/king-county-goes-live-with-customized-evergreen-ils/ |archive-date=2010-10-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

== 功能 ==
* [[OPAC|OPAC]]
*圖書館目錄
*借閱服務
*統計報告

